=== RAW MODEL ANSWER ===
Answer: Step 1: React 1-Boc-piperazine with 1-fluoro-4-nitrobenzene (or 1-chloro-4-nitrobenzene) under SNAr conditions (e.g. K2CO3 or DIPEA, DMF, heat) to give tert-butyl 4-(4-nitrophenyl)piperazine-1-carboxylate, BocN1CCN(c2ccc([N+](=O)[O-])cc2)CC1. | Step 2: Deprotect this intermediate with TFA/CH2Cl2 or HCl/dioxane to furnish 1-(4-nitrophenyl)piperazine, O=[N+]([O-])c1ccc(N2CCNCC2)cc1. | Step 3: N-alkylate that free piperazine nitrogen with tert-butyl (2-bromoethyl)carbamate, BrCCNC(=O)OC(C)(C)C, using base (e.g. K2CO3 or DIPEA, DMF or MeCN, heat) to obtain the target tert-butyl (2-(4-(4-nitrophenyl)piperazin-1-yl)ethyl)carbamate, CC(C)(C)OC(=O)NCCN1CCN(c2ccc([N+](=O)[O-])cc2)CC1.

